hr size=1> In the event that Rotational Mobs spawn on pre-Patch Day, the Rotational Mobs *may* go FFA. <br>
<br>
If a guild that is scheduled for a Rotational Mob, kills the Mob, that is their turn, no FFA needed.<br>
<br>
If a guild cannot, for whatever reason, kill their Rotational Mob, it is considered FFA.  But they do not lose their spot in the Rotation. <br>
<br>
For FFA mobs, the accepted procedure has been: the guild interested in killing the mob will negotiate with the other interested guilds and come to an agreement as to who will get the attempt.<br>
<br>
EXCEPTIONS:<br>
<br>
NToV: due to it's multi-day nature, cannot be considered for FFA by the regularly scheduled Rotation Guild. (See NToV Etiquette for more info).<br>
<br>
The Statue, Idol, AoW:  <br>
<br>
Due to the fact that the Idol/AoW only spawns after the Statue is killed, the guild that has the AoW has precendence over the Statue Spawn, if it's not theirs, so that the AoW is not *lost*.  <br>
<br>
If the guild that has AoW needs to have the Statue killed in a timely manner, and the scheduled guild cannot, they proceed to kill.  The scheduled Guild does not lose their turn, but just gets 'bumped' to the next spawn. <br>
<br>
As always, discussions should take place between the guilds.  Chat Channels should be set up by the interested parties, to facilitate negotiations, and to keep the peace. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm52.showPrevMessage?topicID=7.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm52.showNextMessage?topicID=7.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm52.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/addReply1.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm52.emailToFriend?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm52.threadControl?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm52.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=7.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm52.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=7.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub6.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="therathetravelagencyfrm50">General<option value="therathetravelagencyfrm15">Flame Central<option value="therathetravelagencyfrm11">Guild Re